    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/3d0f2bcbef93d99365242eed0840ef7a.poster.avif?t=1770399860\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/3d0f2bcbef93d99365242eed0840ef7a.webm?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/3d0f2bcbef93d99365242eed0840ef7a.mp4?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Wild Terrain》是一款单人冒险游戏，你将扮演一只野猪。你的动物朋友们神秘失踪，而你必须踏上旅程，将它们全部找回来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要运用力量和智慧，帮助朋友们摆脱各种滑稽、奇怪，甚至危险的境地。在冒险中，你将揭开许多秘密，体验各种活动，并探索隐藏的地区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🐗 主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验野猪的自由生活！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与狐狸、熊和其他动物成为朋友</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由探索充满生机的小型开放世界和故事</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动物们可以跟随你，一起冒险，并听从你的指令</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态天气和温度系统，影响不同环境（雪地、森林、沙漠）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>猛撞破坏挡路的障碍物</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找蘑菇、水果和各种食物</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用各种帽子自定义外观（帽子会影响你的体温）</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/ad0b1dc6e7796c81c7e332c186e03622.poster.avif?t=1770399860\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/ad0b1dc6e7796c81c7e332c186e03622.webm?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/ad0b1dc6e7796c81c7e332c186e03622.mp4?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌲 撞碎并破坏各种物体！利用你的力量推动障碍，发现隐藏的食物、道具和其他重要的秘密。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/bccbc7170b1f590ed10c6980502ee14a.poster.avif?t=1770399860\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/bccbc7170b1f590ed10c6980502ee14a.webm?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/bccbc7170b1f590ed10c6980502ee14a.mp4?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🦊 与朋友们同行！每当你成功救出一位失踪的伙伴，它们都能加入你的旅程，陪伴你一起冒险。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无论你的旅途走到哪里，你都能尽情探索，享受这片世界的乐趣！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/0044512a0230786551264db038ba3982.poster.avif?t=1770399860\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/0044512a0230786551264db038ba3982.webm?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301300/extras/0044512a0230786551264db038ba3982.mp4?t=1770399860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
